====================
Programs
====================
gsm_test.py			(To be removed)
Sends SMS text


ir_test.py
Testing IR break beam.		(To be removed)


led.py
Testing writing to GPIO. 	(To be removed)


main.py INPROGRESS
Temporary(?) main file.  	(Partially just to point out top functions)

cam.py
Takes a picture,stores it on the SD card and calls send_alert.py



door_open.py INPROGRESS
Checks the status of the door pin and returns TRUE if open or FALSE if closed on PIN 16



intrusion_check.py
Will monitor the status of the door while locked and calls cam.py if opened.



lock_door.py INPROGRESS
Sets pin 7 to high "True". This will take Relay K2 High



mail_switch.py INPROGRESS
Return true/HIGH on PIN 32 if mail switch is triggered and calls send_mail.py



readmifare.py
When run, waits for RFID card and texts before exiting program.



send_mail.py
Uses gsm module to send text "You have mail".



send_alert.py
Uses gsm module to send text "You mail has been broken into".



unlock_door.py INPROGRESS
Sets pin 8 to high "True". This will take Relay K1 High



====================
GPIO Pins
====================
PN532:
CS = 18
MOSI = 23
MISO = 24
SCLK = 25

Lock:
OPEN/UNLOCK = 8
CLOSE/LOCK = 7

Door:
Closed = 37
Status = 16

Mail:
Trigger = 36
YesMail = 32

Misc:
LED = 17
